# PigeonLib Architecture

## Boot Sequence

```
main()  [EntryPoint.h]
  в””в”Ђв”Ђ pg::CreateApplication()           (client-defined; registers app-specific systems)
        в””в”Ђв”Ђ Application::Create()
              в””в”Ђв”Ђ Init()
                    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Window::Create()               (platform window + graphics context)
                    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ World::Create()                (ECS registry, clears all state)
                    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ RegisterSystem(AudioPlaybackSystem)
                    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ RegisterSystem(AudioVolumeSystem)
                    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ RegisterSystem(CameraSystem)
                    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ RegisterSystem(ConfigLoaderSystem)
                    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ RegisterSystem(InputSystem)
                    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ RegisterSystem(ResourceManagerSystem)
                    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ RegisterSystem(SaveDataSystem)
                    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ RegisterSystem(SpriteAnimationSystem)
                    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ RegisterSystem(SpriteRenderSystem)
                    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ RegisterSystem(TransformComposeSystem)
                    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ RegisterSystem(TransformResolveSystem)
                    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ RegisterSystem(UIControlSystem)
                    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ RegisterSystem(UIEventSystem)
                    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ RegisterSystem(UIRenderSystem)
                    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ RegisterSystem(WindowConfigSystem)  (reaches the live Window via Application::Get())
                    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Renderer::Init()               (RendererAPI, RenderCommand setup)
                    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ PushOverlay(ImGuiLayer)         [non-test builds only]
                    в””в”Ђв”Ђ m_Initialized = true
  в””в”Ђв”Ђ app.Run()
```

## Per-Frame Update Sequence

```
UpdateApp()
  1. Clock::Restart()           в†’ Timestep (inter-frame delta)
  2. LayerStack::Begin()        вЂ” ImGuiLayer opens a new Dear ImGui frame
  3. LayerStack::OnUpdate(ts)   вЂ” game layers receive delta-time
  4. World::Update(ts)          вЂ” see internal sequence below
  5. LayerStack::End()          вЂ” ImGuiLayer renders accumulated ImGui draw data
  6. Window::OnUpdate()         вЂ” drains OS message queue, then SwapBuffers
```

## World::Update Internal Sequence

```
World::Update(ts)
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ [first frame after RegisterSystem] SortSystems()
  в”‚     в””в”Ђв”Ђ Kahn topological sort; edges from writeSet/inframeAddSet в†’ readSet
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ m_Dispatcher.update()       вЂ” EnTT signal delivery
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ for each system in sorted order:
  в”‚     в””в”Ђв”Ђ system->Update(ts)    вЂ” via CheckedRegistryAccessor
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ ClearEvents()               вЂ” destroys all entities tagged EventComponent
  в””в”Ђв”Ђ FlushDeferredRequests()
        в”њв”Ђв”Ђ apply m_DeferredOneFrameComponents  (emplace + schedule removal)
        в”њв”Ђв”Ђ apply m_DeferredRequests            (persistent emplaces, removes)
        в””в”Ђв”Ђ apply m_DeferredDestroys            (entity destruction)
```

## Platform Event Flow

```
Win32 WM_* message
  в””в”Ђв”Ђ WindowsWindow::WindowProc
        в””в”Ђв”Ђ Application::OnEvent(Event&)
              в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Direct: WindowClose в†’ m_Running=false
              в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Direct: WindowResize в†’ Renderer::OnWindowResize, m_Minimized flag
              в””в”Ђв”Ђ World::EmplaceExternalEvent<XxxEventComponent>()
                    в””в”Ђв”Ђ deferred entity: visible to ECS systems in the NEXT World::Update
```

## Module Interaction Map

```
Platform
  в””в”Ђв”Ђ implements: Window, PlatformInput, GraphicsContext, RendererAPI, Buffer, Shader, Texture
                                в”‚ (abstract interfaces only visible above this line)
                                в–ј
Core
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Application          boot sequence, layer stack, OS event bridge
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ ConfigLoaderSystem   Assets/Engine/Config.json (+ <savedataPath>/Config.json override)  в†’  EngineConfigSingletonComponent  (frame 1 only)
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ InputSystem          input event components  в†’  InputStateSingletonComponent
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ ResourceManagerSystem  manifests (textures/fonts/shaders/ui/sounds/json)  в†’  ResourceMapSingletonComponent  (frame 1 only)
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ SaveDataSystem       EngineConfigSingletonComponent (savedata path) + SetSaveDataRequest (from app)
  в”‚                          в†’  SaveDataSingletonComponent (uuid в†’ json); loads <savedataPath>/SaveSlots/<uuid>.json
  в”‚                            at startup, persists slot files on request
  в””в”Ђв”Ђ WindowConfigSystem   EngineConfigSingletonComponent (window resolution/mode) + SetWindowResolutionRequest
                             в†’  WindowConfigSingletonComponent; applies to the live Window + persists <savedataPath>/Config.json
                                в”‚
                                в–ј
Audio
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ AudioVolumeSystem    EngineConfigSingletonComponent (volumes) + SetAudioVolumeRequest
  в”‚                          в†’  AudioVolumeSingletonComponent (live master/sound/music volumes)
  в””в”Ђв”Ђ AudioPlaybackSystem  ResourceMapSingletonComponent (m_SoundMap) + AudioVolumeSingletonComponent
                             + Play/Stop/Pause/ResumeAudioRequest (from app)
                             в†’  AudioDeviceSingletonComponent (platform mixer); voices keyed by UUID handle

Transform
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ TransformResolveSystem  ResolvedTransformRequest (from app) + CameraTransformRequest
  в”‚                           в†’  PositionComponent, RotationComponent, ScaleComponent, LocalBoundsComponent
  в””в”Ђв”Ђ TransformComposeSystem  Position/Rotation/Scale/LocalBounds  в†’  WorldTransformComponent (matrix + sort key)
                                в”‚ (render bridges read WorldTransformComponent)
                                в–ј
Renderer
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ CameraSystem         SetCameraRequest (from app) + ResizeEvent + PositionComponent
  в”‚                          в†’  OrthographicCameraComponent (zoom/projection) + CameraTransformRequest (pan)
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ SpriteAnimationSystem  SetSpriteAnimationRequest (from app) + SpriteAnimationComponent (app-authored sheet/row/speed) + time
  в”‚                            в†’  SpriteComponent sub-texture (advances the sprite-sheet frame; via pg::SpriteSheet)
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ SpriteRenderSystem     SpriteComponent + WorldTransformComponent  в†’  DrawSpriteInFrameEvent (consumed by Renderer2DSystem)
  в””в”Ђв”Ђ Renderer2DSystem
        reads:  OrthographicCameraComponent (gameplay cam), UICameraSingletonComponent (screen-space UI cam),
                EngineConfigSingletonComponent, ResourceMapSingletonComponent, Draw*InFrameEvent
        writes: RendererDataSingletonComponent в†’ GPU draw calls; world pass (Y-sorted, gameplay cam),
                then UI pass (UI cam, always on top)
                                в–І
                                в”‚ (emits DrawUI*InFrameEvent + UICameraSingletonComponent)
UI  (canvas authored against a reference resolution; scaled to the window per ADR 0005)
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ UIControlSystem      mutation commands + JSON layouts  в†’  BaseComponent, ImageComponent, TextComponent, LayoutContainerComponent, UIClipComponent
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ UIEventSystem        InputStateSingletonComponent + RendererConfigSingletonComponent (scale factor)
  в”‚                          в†’  UIOn*OneFrameComponent (front-most element only, hit-test in logical-canvas units)
  в”‚                          в†’  UIInputCapturedInFrameEvent (gameplay pointer-capture signal over interactive UI)
  в””в”Ђв”Ђ UIRenderSystem       EngineConfigSingletonComponent + WindowResizeEventComponent + BaseComponent
                             + ImageComponent/TextComponent
                             в†’  RendererConfigSingletonComponent (live canvas: scale factor + logical size),
                                UICameraSingletonComponent (screen-space UI camera),
                                DrawUIQuadInFrameEvent, DrawUIStringInFrameEvent
```

## Key Files

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `Code/PigeonLib/Pigeon/Core/Application.h` | Application singleton вЂ” window, layer stack, boot sequence |
| `Code/PigeonLib/Pigeon/Audio/` | Audio module вЂ” SoundClip resource, abstract AudioDevice mixer, the volume + playback systems, request components (see Documentation/ModuleInfo/Audio) |
| `Code/PigeonLib/Platform/Miniaudio/MiniaudioAudioDevice.cpp` | Real audio backend (miniaudio); Testing build uses Platform/Testing/TestingAudioDevice |
| `Code/PigeonLib/Pigeon/ECS/Entity.h` | ECS abstraction layer вЂ” `pg::ecs` names (`Entity`, `null`, `Registry`, `Dispatcher`, `exclude`) over the EnTT library |
| `Code/PigeonLib/Pigeon/ECS/World.h` | ECS World API вЂ” registry, system registration, deferred operations |
| `Code/PigeonLib/Pigeon/ECS/CheckedRegistryAccessor.h` | Accessor API вЂ” View, Get, EmplaceDeferred, EmplaceInframe, EmplaceEvent |
| `Code/PigeonLib/Pigeon/ECS/System.h` | Base System class and SystemAccessDecl struct |
| `Code/PigeonLib/Pigeon/Transform/` | Transform components (Position/Rotation/Scale/LocalBounds/WorldTransform), the resolve + compose systems, and the request types (ADR 0003) |
| `Code/PigeonLib/Pigeon/Renderer/Sprite*.{h,cpp}` | World-space sprites: SpriteComponent (texture + UV sub-rect), SpriteSheet value type (gridв†’UV), SpriteAnimationSystem (advances the sprite-sheet frame from SetSpriteAnimationRequest), SpriteRenderSystem (emits DrawSpriteInFrameEvent). Engine owns the logic; the app sets the data + emits the request |
| `Code/PigeonLib/Pigeon/Renderer/Model.{h,cpp}` | 3D model resource: parses a Wavefront .obj into CPU-side triangle geometry (ModelVertex list + index list); loaded by ResourceManagerSystem into ResourceMapSingletonComponent::m_ModelMap. ModelComponent.h references a loaded model by UUID for world-space 3D scene authoring |
| `Code/PigeonLib/Pigeon/Core/WindowConfigSystem.*` | Window resolution/mode: seeds + owns WindowConfigSingletonComponent, applies to the live Window, persists savedata Config.json (ADR 0004) |
| `Code/PigeonLib/Pigeon/Core/SaveDataSystem.*` | Save-data resource: loads <savedataPath>/SaveSlots/<uuid>.json into SaveDataSingletonComponent at startup; applies + persists SetSaveDataRequest slot updates from the app |
| `Code/PigeonLib/Pigeon/Core/FileUtils.*` | Shared text-file read/write/exists helpers used by the config loader and writer |
| `Code/PigeonLib/Pigeon/Core/Window.h` | Abstract window вЂ” `ApplyWindowConfig(width, height, mode)` resizes / switches windowedв†”borderless-fullscreen |
| `Code/SandboxApp/Sandbox2D.cpp` | Entry point вЂ” CreateApplication() + client system registration |
